data.text:
Port Louis market is well known for its fresh fruits and vegetables, this is probably why most of Mauritians go there. This picture was taken on a Saturday morning, and you will notice how crowded it was. Mauritians love to go there as not only the prices are good but also they are guaranteed to get fresh tropical fruits and vegetables.

Here’s another picture that I have taken outside the market.
